<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="ios_basewidth" id="ios_basewidth">ios_base::width</a></h2>
<div class="level2">
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    streamsize width<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
    streamsize width<span class="br0">&#40;</span> streamsize spec <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

<br/>

</p>

<p>
Manages the minimum number of characters to generate on certain output conversions. The first version returns current field width. The second sets the field width to the given one.
</p>

</div>
